# Streamlit App Walkthrough (High Sensitivity)

## Summary
The finger mode is now set to **High Sensitivity** (Easy to trigger).

## Configuration
- **Threshold**: 0.05 (Low Barrier).
- **Strike**: Even gentle taps will register.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
